{"tid":303981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國外相約翰遜發聲明：英對港承諾如20年前堅定  中方：無意義","createTime":"2017-06-30T14:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T02:23:09.000Z","uid":29804,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"91f665cbf3c7358cd54fef7caa7c9a480c9c11c0","tid":303981,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"1984年的《中英聯合聲明》，現在還有甚麼意義？英國外相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）就香港主權移交20周年發表聲明，強調英國對香港的承諾與20年前一樣堅定，又期望香港未來會有更民主及負責任的政府制度，可是，中國外交部發言人陸慷則稱，《聯合聲明》只是「歷史文件」，「不再具有任何現實意義」，希望國際社會認清現實。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜發表的聲明指出，「我要強調，英國對香港列明在《中英聯合聲明》內的承諾，今天與20年前一樣堅定。我毫不懷疑，香港未來的成功，將取決於聲明內所保障的權利及自由。」他又指「一國兩制」的原則必須繼續遵守，以維持香港生活方式。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，法治、司法獨立及新聞自由，都是香港成功的核心，香港是充滿活力的城市，亦是通往世界上規模最大、增長最快市場的門戶。<br />\n<br />\n不過，陸慷則在外交部例行記者會上指出，「現在香港已經回歸祖國懷抱20年」，「《中英聯合聲明》作為一個歷史文件，不再具有任何現實意義，對中國中央政府對香港特區的管理也不具備任何約束力。英方對回歸後的香港無主權、無治權，無監督權。希望上述人士認清現實。」<br />\n<br />\n綜合報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170630&amp;guid=56898368&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170630%26guid%3D56898368%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=g5IBL8%2FQBGEtBEAJwJh3if1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=ebaf3ab0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170630%26guid%3D56898368%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=84daf7f3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170630&amp;guid=56898368&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"0011993557fcc7fc0710761965a3c8850fb700d5","tid":303981,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧"},{"pid":"afa6cedf85ffe0d3e87208505c6192db963bd3c3","tid":303981,"uid":24980,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"我簽既合同毫無意義，歷史文件"},{"pid":"0577d0820089654aa3c85e63ebe1efc249f25884","tid":303981,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:37:22.000Z","msg":"正式回歸英國"},{"pid":"140ad4be5e7aeacbe9701212267b99996ee350f6","tid":303981,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧🇬🇧"},{"pid":"d52565d74b09f5b6026839d4ac41019939a6ba22","tid":303981,"uid":34029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:41:45.000Z","msg":"快D 派BC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dfeb52d6f4ec9daedcb2bb4cae409514a531cf5","tid":303981,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:42:17.000Z","msg":"莊漢生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4f0e431e7e38f41d7b0b7ba4e9ec83a2c7f559","tid":303981,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:42:47.000Z","msg":"聲明國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834c6b051e0933b2c6f629340c0c97c1540b0e1e","tid":303981,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"承諾誠信，不再具有任何現實意義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f536c2590af1553e961911b3f25848ebf425147","tid":303981,"uid":4281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"祖國🇬🇧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3725160acf01af35384dbf6c0715d3cbccb8d4c","tid":303981,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:47:54.000Z","msg":"中美三個聯合公報也是歷史文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4595ae321f85